title: FER-DS
subtitle: Facial Emotion Recognition Dataset
description: The data consists of 48x48 pixel grayscale images of faces. The task is to categorize each face based on the emotion shown in the facial expression in to one of four categories (0=Angry, 1=Happy, 2=Neutral, 3=Surprise).
